data.description: Check out this newly remodeled home that was built in 1918 is a perfect blend of modern updates and historic charm. There is no HOA but is walkable distance to downtown to enjoy the restaurants and shops that Delta has to offer. It is a 2-bedroom, Primary being on the main level and the loft style room upstairs, both with attached baths. This home has updated Vinyl floors and wood burning fireplace seated in the living room. With a covered porch and a deck, there is plenty of space to enjoy sitting outside. The gate to access the back yard is wide enough to put an RV in the back. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your new home!
